ygData.messageBody:
Hi all,

I have 2 EQ accounts that is up for sale.

First account contains a level 45 druid, a level 30
magician, a level 20 warrior and a level 6 Shadow
Knight. All are equipped with good items.

Second account contains a level 45 wizard and some
lower level characters that I have not played much.
The level 45 wizard is equipped with good items.

Reason for selling: I'm leaving the game and its such
a waste to throw away 1 year's time spent in the game.

Please reply to steven_wck@... if interested.

Rgds,

Steven
